{"tid":2298538,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"碧咸回歸《FIFA 21》傳收天價酬勞　仲誇張過全盛時期落場踢","createTime":"2020-11-24T06:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T16:56:20.000Z","uid":16659,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"5f1e2730155f2775e0cec7c4b946e3b4f79d7ccf","tid":2298538,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:20:45.000Z","msg":"昔日英國「足球金童」碧咸（David Beckham），在曼聯與洛杉磯銀河隊都曾享受過傲人的身價，但他近日傳出將在PlayStation與Xbox的最新的FIFA 21中以「傳奇球星」的身分亮相，廠商原本已豪擲「3年3000萬英鎊」的酬勞，他不滿意、爭取往上加，據傳最後以3年4000萬英鎊（約港幣4.1億）成交，比他以往真的落場踢足球的身價還要高。<br />\n<br />\n英國媒體報導，碧咸過去在曼聯是周薪10萬鎊，13年前應邀赴洛杉磯銀河隊的身價是5年2500萬英鎊，都遠不及這次賣「身」FIFA咁豐厚，也證明碧咸這個品牌在「辣妹」碧咸嫂的苦心炒作下，已經成為吸金實力不輸時尚精品的超級名牌，體力上已不如球壇後輩的碧咸，也能夠更輕鬆吸金。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201123/407527239068946432268430.png/Qt1_2PeTy1NRO4HEBsVXD7ST-9YQU1_wSPUm-Ej1Jvg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201123%2F407527239068946432268430.png%2FQt1_2PeTy1NRO4HEBsVXD7ST-9YQU1_wSPUm-Ej1Jvg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f6a6f98c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed38bc5a7efc820c3838cc98e78d268b16fba6b6","tid":2298538,"uid":68689,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:26:19.000Z","msg":"86<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a08ad4db908af3c018128e59c6f85b7f7bea66e","tid":2298538,"uid":196924,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:27:10.000Z","msg":"Legend (86)"},{"pid":"6fce2433e049ad6fa7052b115de17f59ba4149d3","tid":2298538,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:28:29.000Z","msg":"pes又唔知俾幾多？"},{"pid":"c5f584de762e62d269e2dd3f9198282bfcafdf9f","tid":2298538,"uid":39208,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"ed38bc5a7efc820c3838cc98e78d268b16fba6b6","tid":229853